Uses of Package
uml

  • Packages that use uml 
    Package Description
    inputmdxml
    Contains the main converter class which calls the actual converter classes
    inputmdxml.converter.element
    Contains converter classes converting PackagedElements and their child elements to UmlElements
    inputmdxml.converter.relationship
    Contains converter classes converting PackagedElements and their child elements to UmlRelationships
    inputmdxml.temporary
    Contains auxiliary elements to store temporary conversion results
    uml
    This package contains all model classes of the UML representation.
    uml.converterinterface
    This package provides interfaces for an input representation converter and the input representation.
    umlcode
    Contains the main converter class and TemporaryModel as a temporary storage of converted elements.
    umlcode.converter.element
    Contains converter classes for UmlElements and UmlPackages
    umlcode.converter.relationship
    Contains converter classes for UmlRelationships to map supplier and client CodeElements of interface realizations and generalizations to each other.
  • Classes in uml used by inputmdxml 
    Class Description
    UmlModel
    Represents the UML model with its UmlPackages, UmlElements and UmlRelationships
    UmlParent
    Interface implemented by the classes of the model to reference a parent class
